ed. See [answer](http://answers.gazebosim.org/question/6239/gazebo-30-system-plugin-tutorial-crashing/).", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Init() is called before the rendering engine is initialized, see <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"https://bitbucket.org/osrf/gazebo/issue/1212/init-of-gui-system-plugin-called-before\" rel=\"nofollow\">Issue 1212</a></p>\n<p>As workaround until the issue is fixed: initialize rendering related variables after a rendering event has been published. See <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"http://answers.gazebosim.org/question/6239/gazebo-30-system-plugin-tutorial-crashing/\" rel=\"nofollow\">answer</a>.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "resolved", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2014-06-13T11:50:24.624167+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2016-01-29T06:26:57.601075+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 8}